        public void setElementSpacing(java.lang.String elementSpacing)
        Method set anatomicalSpacing property for meta image.
        Parameters:
        elementSpacing - string representing physical distance between elements(voxels). Distance between elements is specified in three directions - x, y, z in [mm] and separated with space: setElementSpacing("0.7 0.7 1");
